---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="relative bg-charcoal text-bone/80 pt-32 pb-12 overflow-hidden clip-slant-footer z-20">
  
  <!-- Background subtle bloom -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[10%] w-[35vw] h-[35vw] rounded-full bg-olive-500/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 max-w-7xl relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-8 pb-16 border-b border-bone/10">
      
      <!-- Brand Description Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <a href="#inicio" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-olive-500 to-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center text-bone font-serif font-bold text-lg shadow-md">
            CR
          </div>
          <span class="text-bone font-serif font-bold text-xl tracking-wide">
            Coronado <span class="text-gold-500 font-sans font-light">Real Estate</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="font-sans text-xs md:text-sm text-bone/60 leading-relaxed max-w-sm mt-2">
          Desarrollo residencial premium en Saltillo, Coahuila. Creamos espacios habitacionales de alta calidad, sustentables y con garantía de plusvalía para tu patrimonio.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Social Networks Icons -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-4">
          <a href="#" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-bone/5 hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-charcoal flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 text-bone/80" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-bone/5 hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-charcoal flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 text-bone/80" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Quick Navigation Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <h4 class="font-serif font-bold text-base text-bone tracking-wide">Navegación</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 font-sans text-xs md:text-sm text-bone/60">
          <li><a href="#inicio" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
          <li><a href="#amenidades" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Amenidades</a></li>
          <li><a href="#beneficios" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Diferenciales</a></li>
          <li><a href="#galeria" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Galería</a></li>
          <li><a href="#testimonios" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Reseñas</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contacto" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Info Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <h4 class="font-serif font-bold text-base text-bone tracking-wide">Ubicación y Ventas</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-xs md:text-sm text-bone/60">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Saltillo, Coahuila, México. Zona Norte de Crecimiento.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <a href="mailto:info@coronadore.com" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">info@coronadore.com</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.94.725l.548 2.2a1 1 0 00.099.281l-.918.918a1.593 1.593 0 00-.32 1.01c.033.882.234 1.733.586 2.507a1.593 1.593 0 001.01.32l.918-.918a1 1 0 00.281-.099l2.2.548a1 1 0 01.725.94V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            <a href="https://wa.me/528441234567" target="_blank" class="hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">+52 844 123 4567</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom copyright / branding watermark -->
    <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-bone/40 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold relative">
      <div>
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Coronado Real Estate. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </div>
      <div>
        Diseño por Coronado Real Estate UI/UX Lab
      </div>
      
      <!-- Big watermark branding behind -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-[-10px] right-0 font-serif font-black text-[7vw] leading-none text-bone/[0.02] select-none pointer-events-none translate-y-6">
        Coronado
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
